{"_id":"8Yo1XQzxLKMg5cUZ","name":"FW Fishing Docks","permission":{"default":2,"NbkKMYLLsYqKniCN":3,"S3eL5TZKAP0Ahfct":3},"folder":"yp4hsh8hVGo81uAi","sort":62501,"flags":{},"content":"<p>In Felwarren's earliest days, some bright pioneer introduced freshwater fish to its lake. Now the town gets a meaningful fraction of its food from fishing. The fishermen mostly dock here, which is also located next to a plaza for a fish market.</p>"}
